10-year mortality, causes of death and cardiovascular comorbidities in 
idiopathic normal pressure hydrocephalus.

Eklund SA(1), Israelsson H(2), Brunström M(3), Forsberg K(4), Malm J(4).

Author information:
(1)Department of Clinical Science, Neurosciences, Umeå University, Umeå, Sweden. 
Sanna.Eklund@umu.se.
